==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|midwives}}
# A person, [[usually]] a [[woman]], who is [[train]]ed to [[assist]] women in [[childbirth]], but who is not a [[physician]].
#(''by extension'') Someone who assists in bringing about some result or project.

====Translation====
'''person who assists women in childbirth'''
