{{mid}}
*Norwegian: [[jordmor]] {{m}},{{f}}
*Portuguese: [[parteira]] {{f}}
{{bottom}}

===Verb===
{{en-verb|midwiv|es}}
;or
{{en-verb|midwif|es}}
# {{transitive}} To act as a midwife.

